OL,4,Cstalking of Madeleine McCann's family
OL,6,FTwo women have appeared in court
OL,7,Fcharged with the alleged stalking of
OL,8,FMadeleine McCann's family.
OL,10,FJulia Wandel, a 23-year-old Polish
OL,11,Fnational accused of stalking the
OL,12,Ffamily of Madeleine McCann, has been
OL,13,Frefused bail during a hearing at
OL,14,FLeicester Crown Court on Friday, 28
OL,15,FMarch.
OL,17,FJudge Timothy Spencer KC ruled that no
OL,18,Fdetails from the bail application can
OL,19,Fbe reported, ahead of a plea and trial
OL,20,Fpreparation hearing listed to take
OL,21,Fplace at the same court on April 22.
