OL,3,CTwo women appear in court over alleged
OL,4,Cstalking of Madeleine McCann's family
OL,6,FKaren Spragg, of Caerau in Cardiff,
OL,7,Fwas charged on Thursday with one count
OL,8,Fof stalking involving serious alarm or
OL,9,Fdistress between May 3, 2024, and
OL,10,FFebruary 21 this year.
OL,12,FThe indictment alleged Spragg made
OL,13,Fcalls, sent letters and attended the
OL,14,Fhome address of Mr and Mrs McCann.
