OL,3,CTwo women appear in court over alleged
OL,4,Cstalking of Madeleine McCann's family
OL,6,FAppearing at Leicester Magistrates'
OL,7,FCourt on Friday, Spragg, wearing a
OL,8,Fbeige tracksuit and blue Crocs and
OL,9,Fcarrying a red bag, spoke to confirm
OL,10,Fher name and address during the 10-
OL,11,Fminute hearing and indicated she would
OL,12,Fnot be entering a plea.
OL,14,FChair of the bench Elizabeth Needham
OL,15,Freleased Spragg on bail with
OL,16,Fconditions not to contact Mr and Mrs
OL,17,FMcCann, their children and two family
OL,18,Ffriends, not to enter Leicestershire
OL,19,Funless attending court and to live and
OL,20,Fsleep at her home address.
