OL,4,Cstalking of Madeleine McCann's family
OL,6,FShe was ordered to appear alongside
OL,7,FWandel at Leicester Crown Court on
OL,8,FApril 22.
OL,10,FMrs Needham said: "Your case is going
OL,11,Fto the crown court and the date for
OL,12,Fthat is April 22. You have heard the
OL,13,Fbail conditions, if you break any of
OL,14,Fthose you are likely to be arrested.
OL,16,F"If you do not attend court that is
OL,17,Flikely to be a breach of your bail. In
OL,18,Fthe meantime, keep in contact with
OL,19,Fyour solicitor."
